---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="always tired? here’s how to fix it naturally"
  description="if you feel tired all the time, learn what’s causing it and how to restore natural energy through rhythm and habits."
>
  <section class="page-hero section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">guide</p>
      <h1>always tired? here’s what’s causing it</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        low energy is usually not random — it comes from a breakdown in daily rhythm.
      </p>
      <p class="lead">
        fix the system, and energy starts to return naturally.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>common causes</h2>
        <div class="content-list">
          <p>inconsistent sleep schedule</p>
          <p>lack of morning sunlight</p>
          <p>low physical movement</p>
          <p>overstimulation (screens, media)</p>
          <p>unstable eating patterns</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>what’s happening</h2>
        <p>
          your body runs on rhythm. when sleep, light, movement, and food are inconsistent,
          your energy system becomes unstable.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section accent-section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <h2>quick reset</h2>
      <div class="content-block">
        <p>fix your wake-up time</p>
        <p>get sunlight early</p>
        <p>walk daily</p>
        <p>eat consistent meals</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="y2k-panel feature-card">
        <div class="panel-heading-row">
          <p class="panel-kicker">optional tool</p>
          <span class="panel-stamp">energy</span>
        </div>
        <h2>support natural energy</h2>
        <p>
          morning sunlight and consistent rhythm are the strongest natural ways to restore energy.
        </p>
        <a href="/sunlight" class="button">learn about sunlight</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="y2k-panel feature-card">
        <div class="panel-heading-row">
          <p class="panel-kicker">related</p>
          <span class="panel-stamp">system</span>
        </div>
        <h2>go deeper</h2>
        <div class="content-list">
          <p><a href="/cant-focus">fix focus issues</a></p>
          <p><a href="/brain-fog">clear brain fog</a></p>
          <p><a href="/how-to-fix-sleep">fix sleep first</a></p>
          <p><a href="/start-here">understand the full system</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
